{"words":[{"word":"paintings","count":2},{"word":"wait","count":2},{"word":"leaves","count":2},{"word":"usually","count":2},{"word":"take","count":2},{"word":"long","count":2},{"word":"return","count":2},{"word":"okay","count":2},{"word":"around","count":2},{"word":"art","count":2},{"word":"nope","count":2},{"word":"oh","count":2},{"word":"buy","count":1},{"word":"works","count":1},{"word":"huh","count":1},{"word":"bad","count":1},{"word":"nothing","count":1},{"word":"books","count":1},{"word":"though","count":1},{"word":"easiest","count":1},{"word":"run","count":1},{"word":"either","count":1},{"word":"helped","count":1},{"word":"guess","count":1},{"word":"call","count":1},{"word":"friends","count":1},{"word":"gifted","count":1},{"word":"painting","count":1},{"word":"somewhere","count":1},{"word":"ah","count":1},{"word":"fancy","count":1},{"word":"connoisseurs","count":1},{"word":"girl","count":1},{"word":"paint","count":1},{"word":"recall","count":1},{"word":"anything","count":1},{"word":"noteworthy","count":1},{"word":"mention","count":1},{"word":"remember","count":1},{"word":"talking","count":1},{"word":"making","count":1},{"word":"step","count":1},{"word":"into","count":1},{"word":"whatever","count":1},{"word":"little","count":1},{"word":"excursions","count":1},{"word":"stirred","count":1},{"word":"unstable","count":1},{"word":"frequencies","count":1},{"word":"warned","count":1},{"word":"listen","count":1},{"word":"usual","count":1},{"word":"bit","count":1},{"word":"hunting","count":1},{"word":"gigs","count":1},{"word":"everyday","count":1},{"word":"grind","count":1},{"word":"many","count":1},{"word":"jobs","count":1},{"word":"enough","count":1},{"word":"scrape","count":1},{"word":"uh","count":1},{"word":"haha","count":1},{"word":"reminded","count":1},{"word":"sell","count":1},{"word":"pigments","count":1},{"word":"occasionally","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Who are you?","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"If it's her paintings you're after, why are you here?","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"I see. Just wait for her here. When she leaves, it usually doesn't take long for her to return.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"You're here to buy paintings? That's not how this works. Go on, get out of here.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Huh? Okay then, my bad.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"...It's nothing. Just wait for her here. When she leaves, it usually doesn't take long for her to return.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Know her? We go way back. She's... okay in our books. Though she hasn't had the easiest run either, she helped us out a while back.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Guess you could call us friends. She even gifted us a painting. It's somewhere around here...","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Ah, here it is! We're no fancy connoisseurs, but even we can tell that girl can paint!","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Can't recall anything noteworthy...","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Well, now that you mention it, I do remember her talking about making art you could \"step into\" or whatever.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"But her little art excursions stirred up some unstable Frequencies. We warned her, but did she listen? Nope.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Us? Oh, the usual. A bit of hunting, some gigs here and there. Just the everyday grind.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Nope, not many jobs around, just enough to scrape by.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000},{"text":"Uh... Oh! Right, haha, you reminded me. We do make and sell pigments occasionally.","quest_name":"True Colors","quest_id":311000000}]}